      "acceptanceCriteria": "Achieved level must meet or exceed required level for model risk level 3.",
      "rationale": "Mesh convergence studies were performed on the pedicle screw and rod assembly. Quantities of interest (peak von Mises stress, construct stiffness) showed less than 5% change upon mesh refinement, confirming adequate discretization."
    },
